did.abstract: The records consist of reports, correspondence, minutes, and subject files documenting the actions and deliberations of the Yale College Course of Study Committee.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-D (YRG 9-D), Records of Yale College committees.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the records is partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use

Copyright status for other collection materials is unknown. prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Course of Study Committee, Yale College, Records (RU 595). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of reports, correspondence, minutes, and subject files documenting the actions and deliberations of the Yale College Course of Study Committee.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.
